title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2008-13 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution X Projector Headlights
description: This video tutorial demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder Auto's LED DRL projector headlights for 2008-13 Mitsubishi Lancer and Lancer Evolution X (Evo X) models both with and without the factory Mitsubishi HID system. These projector headlights feature bright LED daytime running lights and are compatible with the self-levelling function of HID-equipped models.
tags: Spyder Headlights, projector lights, Mitsubishi Lancer, Evolution X, Evo X, how to install, spyder lights
